data.description: This move-in ready 3BR 1BA brick ranch home is awaiting new residents. The living room features a cozy and comfortable atmosphere. There's tile throughout plus  neutral paint throughout the interior. A cute kitchen with all appliances and ample cabinet space. All bedrooms are a nice size. Have fun in the large, level backyard. Home features a metal roof. Hurry! This home won't last!
